    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great with only minor surface blemishes and small stone chips consistent with its age, while the interior is clean with minimal signs of wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car is solid, starts reliably, and drives smoothly, though it may soon require routine maintenance like a brake pad replacement. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
