    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels brand new without the showroom price tag? This beauty is in absolute mint condition\u2014I've truly babied it since day one! It drives like a dream and looks like it just rolled off the lot. No scratches, no smells, just pure perfection inside and out. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love every mile in it. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
