    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2020 BMW M2 Competition that defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen a drop of rain. The Hockenheim Silver Metallic paint is laser-straight and wears a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring a deep, mirror-like finish free of swirls or stone chips. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule: the Black Dakota leather seats retain their factory-firm bolsters with no creasing, and the carbon fiber accents are devoid of even the slightest hairline scratch. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, supported by a comprehensive folder of dealership service records. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is a rare, no-excuses example for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
